settings.description: This is just for fun. You can fly around with the power up.
I wanted to do a very complete level 0-0
Just a simple traditional level with note blocks, try to find all 5 e-Coins!

A switch abundance! And surprisingly, you need to use them..

--Intended with any character--
Iggy's refined airship, most likely to stop Mario but maybe he just wanted a new fancier airship eh?
I realized that many support the series of difficult or almost impossible to win challenges, Mario escapes from the pipe with water then he goes inside to run because a wave of air chases him!...
You need to master number block swimming to beat this one. Watch out for Big Bass! Now with an E-Coin.
This is the third part of the series that makes us giggle the most while we lose. This is a level with a lot of trolling, something that is no longer funny but sad
